<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Quedlinburg</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Unterstützung des Fritz Krebs, Bürger zu Nürnberg, und bittet weiterhin um Förderung aller Nürnberger.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_244" id="121r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_244_r1l6">Der Stat cʒu Quedlaborgh </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_244_r1l7"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Fricʒ krebs <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> . vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l8">daʒ Jm ewr erſame <expan>freuntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> in ſeinen <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l9"><expan>handlu<ex>n</ex>gen</expan> bey euch gar <expan>fürderlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd hılfflıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l10">gevveſen ſey vnd euch <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gen Jm beweiſet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l11">habt / des vvir <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntſchaft fleiſʒi </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l13"><expan>klıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dancken / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_244_line_1571303448912_591">euch </ab></add> dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>fricʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l14">krebs vnd auch <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>kauffleute<ex>n</ex></expan> vvo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l15">
<del rend="strikethrough"> ob </del> die fürbaſmer 
<del rend="strikethrough">bey </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_244_line_1571303551462_610">cʒu </ab></add> euch 
<del rend="strikethrough">icht cʒeſch </del> kömen in Jren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l16"><expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet <expan>günſtiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l19">vnd Jn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> beweiſen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_244_r1l18">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> Als Jr wolte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l20">daʒ vvir den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey vns tun ſolten / ob das ʒe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l21">ſchulden köme / vnd als vvir des gut getrawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l22">cʒu euch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir v̈mb euch vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_244_r1l23">dıe <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wıllıklıch vnd <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> verdıenen <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_244" id="121r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Quedlaborgh </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
                        Fricz Krebs, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie daz im ewr ersame
                                <expan>freunts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> in seinen
                            <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>handlu<ex>n</ex>gen</expan>
                        bey euch gar <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und hilfflich gewesen sey
                        und euch <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gen im beweiset habt, des wir
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntschaft
                            <expan>fleisziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dancken. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <add>euch</add> dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> Krebs und auch
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>kauffleute<ex>n</ex></expan>, wo
                        die fürbasmer <add>czu</add> euch kömen, in iren
                            <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet
                            <expan>günstiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen und in
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> beweisen, <add>durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add>, als ir wolte, daz wir den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey uns tun solten, ob das ze schulden
                        köme, und als wir des gut getrawen czu euch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                        Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb euch und die
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> williklich und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        verdienen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
